Info Workflow
widgets_values:
STEPS 
6-10 good baseline 
15-25 for maximum quality 

CFG 3.5 bOth 
1 CFG increases Speed by 2x but reduces prompt adherence and quality 
(essentially removing negative prompting) 

Boundary
For Wan 2.2 Text2Video, this value should be 0.875. 
For Wan 2.2 Image2Video, this value should be 0.9. 
Using other values might still work. 

SAMPLER 
euler - simple 

SIGMA SHIFT 
T2V 8-12 (12) 
I2V 5-8 (5) 
T2I 1-5 

Higher shift value will make noise removal slower in the start of the generation
and with lower shift values, the noise removal will start off quicker.
